OL,3,CJoey Barton denied bail over assault
OL,4,Ccharge
OL,6,FFormer footballer Joey Barton has been
OL,7,Fdenied bail following a court hearing.
OL,9,FThe 43-year-old, of Widnes, Cheshire,
OL,10,Fhas been in custody since 10 March,
OL,11,Fwhen he appeared at Liverpool
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court charged with
OL,13,Fassault occasioning grievous bodily
OL,14,Fharm with intent.
OL,16,FFollowing a hearing, on 20 March,
OL,17,FJudge David Potter refused a bail
OL,18,Fapplication for Barton at Liverpool
OL,19,FCrown Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
