OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774033868
OL,3,CJoey Barton denied bail over assault
OL,4,Ccharge
OL,6,FThe majority of the bail hearing was
OL,7,Fheld in private, before the judge
OL,8,Fannounced his ruling in open court.
OL,10,FBarton, who did not attend the hearing
OL,11,Fbut was represented by Simon Csoka KC,
OL,12,Fwill next appear at Liverpool Crown
OL,13,FCourt on 7 April.
OL,15,FHe and co-defendant Gary O'Grady, 50,
OL,16,Fof Huyton, Merseyside, are accused of
OL,17,Fattacking Kevin Lynch near Huyton and
OL,18,FPrescot Golf Club on 8 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
