PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774033868
OL,3,CJoey Barton denied bail over assault
OL,4,Ccharge
OL,6,FO'Grady was released on conditional
OL,7,Fbail after the magistrates' court
OL,8,Fhearing.
OL,10,FFormer Manchester City and QPR
OL,11,Fmidfielder Barton has one England cap
OL,12,Fand also played for Newcastle,
OL,13,FRangers, Burnley and Marseille.
OL,15,FHe now hosts podcast Common Sense With
OL,16,FJoey Barton, which is described as an
OL,17,F"unfiltered" look at issues in sport,
OL,18,Fsociety, politics and more.
